rows.label: tlk45200153_04_msg0001
rows.name:
Everyone's saying the Superbia Divine Beast
isn't going to be alive for much longer.

rows.label: tlk45200153_04_msg0002
rows.name:
Superbia's a big place... Apart from
Alba Margen, there are cities around
its right shoulder and belly as well.

rows.label: tlk45200153_04_msg0003
rows.name:
We can't all move to Gula at once,
and apparently they don't even have
enough houses there for everyone...

rows.label: tlk45200153_04_msg0004
rows.name:
Apparently nobody was expecting the
Divine Beast's life to end so soon.

rows.label: tlk45200153_04_msg0005
rows.name:
D'you think we're all done for?
Is there nothing anyone can do...?

rows.label: tlk45200153_04_msg0006
rows.name:
Thanks. If there's anything you can do,
please try to help everyone!
